title: EYL #95 Final Call feat. Rizza Islam
itunes:title: EYL #95 Final Call feat. Rizza Islam
description:
Rizza Islam is currently one of the most powerful and important voices online for social, economic, and political activism. He has been featured on a long list of publications and shows but as a native of Compton, California, his community work spans years before he became an online sensation. In episode 95, Rizza sat down with us to discuss a long list of topics. He talked about the devaluation of American currency, The Federal Reserve, group economics, gentrification, politics, and more.
